profile_positions.description:
Worked as a projectleader and researcher within the Real Estate & Facility Management department of Royal FloraHolland. Responsible for the locations Aalsmeer, Naaldwijk and Rijnsburg. Our department is responsible for projects higher than €250.000.

I was responsible for the following projects:
- Fire-safety certification on all locations;
- Feasibility study on the economic, process implementation and technical capabilities of using temporary cold storage solutions for our logistic operations together with WFBR and other suppliers, my advice was approved by management and will be realised this year;
- Work motivation study on increasing the motivation, openness to change and collaboration between co-workers enterprise-wide using cross-department councils (in collaboration with AFI KLM E&M);
- Assessment study for initiating a new enterprise-wide building/space management system;
- Cold storage location registration following regulations on all locations.

Other projects I was connected to included:
- Royal FloraHolland CO2 neutral 2025;
- Transition of hard services from in-house to CBRE;
- VVE's.

